  - dialogue:
    - ' First, turn on the weighing scale using the top button.'
    - Then place the tray on the metal plate on top of the weighing scale.
    - ' Remember to press the lower button on the weight to reset it and make sure
      it is set zero. '
    - Place the fish in the tray and note its weight
    - Then press the weight button on the registering device and input the weight,
      then press the equals button.
